|GKB-- The Druids -------------------------------------------------|000

    In the world of Geshtai, there are many powers, but
the oldest of these is Gaea, the incarnation of Nature
itself.  The sea and stone, the storm and sun,
the raw power of fire and lightning and wind,
and the animals and plants of Geshtai... all of
this is Gaea's domain.

    Gaea has no clerics, but she does have followers,
and the druids are counted among their number.  A
group of secretive warrior-priests, they study the
mysteries of Gaea and draw upon her power in their
efforts to serve Nature.  Gaea's power is broad in
scope, and each druid may develop different rituals
and invocations -- yet they do not rely solely on
magic, and can fight as fiercely as any cleric.

    If you would join their ranks, seek out the
circle of stones hidden in the forest west of town.

